    <h6>Ways in which Christians promote and protect animals, fish and birds</h6>
    <ul>
        <p>There are different strategies for taking care of God’s creatures like</p>
        <li>Constructing good houses for domestic animals</li>
        <li>Fencing our farms well to keep away wild animals</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Animals need food, shelter and security to be healthy.</p>

